02 February 2012

Kate & Rob tie the knot...

   [P1050209b.jpg]
   [P1050207b.jpg]
   Congratulations Kate and Rob!
   The cake is a white on white brush embroidered to match the lace on the
   beautiful brides dress.
   The cake was served as dessert and was milk choc mud, white choc mud
   and dark choc mud :-) Pin It

