Judiann is 60.....

   [P1050872c.jpg]
   [P1050875c.jpg]
   [P1050867c.jpg]
   A very special cake this week. My mum turned 60!!!!! Happy birthday mum
   :)
   Mum had no say in the design so I went with elegant and pretty, just
   like her.
   The cake is a red velvet cake with white chocolate ganache. Pin It

